#harvest23 #caseih #jmharvest #cornharvest #patrioticfarmer

Happy New Year! Thanks to everyone for following my crazy journey across rural WI capturing farmers at work. Looking forward to 2024, I will be learning to use 2 new cameras. I had to replace my reliable a6500 in October with the new a6700, and I traded my A7R4 for an A7R5 last week. I'm excited to see what the new AI powered auto focus system can do. Have a safe and prosperous 2024!
